= **SCP-7785** - Mr. Lengthwise and Mr. Longways by [[*user PeppersGhost]]

-----

[[=]]
**[[[peppersghost|More by this author]]]**
[[/=]]
[[include :scp-wiki:component:author-label-source end=--]]

= [[image https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/scp-7785/ScratchedAnomBar.png]]


= [[image https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/scp-7785/Longboys1alt.png]]


[[div class="frametop"]]
= [[image https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/scp-7785/LongboysFrame3.png]]
[[/div]]


[[div class="frametop-mobile"]]
